---
title: Pork Enchilada Casserole with Spinach Side Salad
description: This dish packs all the flavours of a Tex-Mex feast into a hearty casserole! We've hidden wholesome veggies in this family-friendly oven-bake and paired it with a vibrant side salad that grown-up palates will appreciate!
